    <string name="settings_about_body">HighlightCam uses on-device AI to detect soccer goals and crowd reactions. It continuously buffers video, and when a highlight is detected, it stitches segments into a single MP4 clip saved to your gallery.\n\nVisual detection uses a YOLOv8n model running on TensorFlow Lite. Audio detection uses Goertzel frequency analysis to identify referee whistles and crowd spikes.</string>

